stackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe4fa8b9c-e6d8-47d3-914e-1eb87be58d30_796x448.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>他们继续表明，与妊娠相关的孕产妇死亡原因（如子痫和羊水栓塞）有所下降，而与妊娠无关的死亡原因（如高血压和糖尿病）却有所增加。这表明我们正在关注孕产妇死亡报告方式的变化，而不是美国产科护理的恶化</p><p>但这并没有让美国医疗系统完全摆脱困境。即使在报告发生变化之前，美国孕产妇死亡率就略高于大多数富裕国家： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F991ba532-6966-4645-9f63-7c5c13602371_1020x720.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F991ba532-6966-4645-9f63-7c5c13602371_1020x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F991ba532-6966-4645-9f63-7c5c13602371_1020x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F991ba532-6966-4645-9f63-7c5c13602371_1020x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F991ba532-6966-4645-9f63-7c5c13602371_1020x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F991ba532-6966-4645-9f63-7c5c13602371_1020x720.jpeg" width="1020" height="720" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/991ba532-6966-4645-9f63-7c5c13602371_1020x720.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:720,&quot;width&quot;:1020,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:95630,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F991ba532-6966-4645-9f63-7c5c13602371_1020x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F991ba532-6966-4645-9f63-7c5c13602371_1020x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F991ba532-6966-4645-9f63-7c5c13602371_1020x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F991ba532-6966-4645-9f63-7c5c13602371_1020x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>这并不像英联邦图表那么糟糕，但也不是很好（韩国到底怎么了？？）。美国在降低孕产妇死亡率方面仍有大量工作要做。但就像 2010 年代的许多衰落论叙述一样，这个故事并没有我们想象的那么戏剧化。</p><h4>美国最愚蠢的经济统计数据再次来袭</h4><p>说到夸大的危机叙事，大多数美国人“靠工资过活”的想法怎么样？你看到很多人都提出这样的说法，包括令人尊敬的伯尼·桑德斯： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F016ed3d6-e60d-413c-a4b4-26e87f1eec67_917x372.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F016ed3d6-e60d-413c-a4b4-26e87f1eec67_917x372.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F016ed3d6-e60d-413c-a4b4-26e87f1eec67_917x372.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F016ed3d6-e60d-413c-a4b4-26e87f1eec67_917x372.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F016ed3d6-e60d-413c-a4b4-26e87f1eec67_917x372.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F016ed3d6-e60d-413c-a4b4-26e87f1eec67_917x372.jpeg" width="676" height="274.2333696837514" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/016ed3d6-e60d-413c-a4b4-26e87f1eec67_917x372.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:372,&quot;width&quot;:917,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:676,&quot;bytes&quot;:80056,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F016ed3d6-e60d-413c-a4b4-26e87f1eec67_917x372.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F016ed3d6-e60d-413c-a4b4-26e87f1eec67_917x372.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F016ed3d6-e60d-413c-a4b4-26e87f1eec67_917x372.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F016ed3d6-e60d-413c-a4b4-26e87f1eec67_917x372.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>现在，我支持劳工部的规则改变。但大多数美国人“靠工资过活”的陈词滥调确实需要退休。从经济统计数据来看，这是最假的。</p><p>基本上，发生的事情是像 LendingClub 这样的私营公司<a href="https://www.bankrate.com/finance/credit-cards/living-paycheck-to-paycheck-statistics/">四处询问人们</a>“你是靠工资生活吗？”大多数人都说是的。然后这些数字就会<a href="https://www.cnbc.com/2023/10/31/62percent-of-americans-still-live-paycheck-to-paycheck-amid-inflation.html">被财经媒体报道，</a>就好像它们是某种经济事实一样。但他们不是。因为“靠工资生活”没有明确的含义。</p><p> “靠工资生活”是否意味着：</p><ul><li><p>你的存款为零？</p></li><li><p>您的积蓄太少而无法舒适吗？</p></li><li><p>您的<em>流动性</em>储蓄为零或不足——银行里的现金，而不是您退休账户中的股票？</p></li><li><p>您通常一个月内没有积累任何财富吗？</p></li><li><p>您在退休帐户中存钱并每月还清抵押贷款，但您不增加流动现金？</p></li><li><p>如果没有下一份薪水，您就无法支付每月的账单吗？</p></li><li><p>您只是期待每个月收到薪水吗？</p></li></ul><p>没人知道。对于许多回答“是”的不同人来说，这可能意味着许多不同的事情。因此，请停止引用“薪水到薪水”的数字。这是没有意义的。</p><p>事实证明，一些经济学家确实研究了关于美国人拥有多少财务缓冲的明确数据。 2022 年消费者财务调查发现，约 98.6% 的美国家庭拥有支票账户或类似账户，这些账户中的金额中位数<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/great-news-about-american-wealth">为 8000 美元</a>。 2016 年，约 76% 的美国人<a href="https://www.federalreserve.gov/econres/notes/feds-notes/assessing-families-liquid-savings-using-the-survey-of-consumer-finances-20181119.html">银行存款超过 400 美元</a>——较 2000 年代中期有所增加。 2013 年至 2019 年间，表示愿意选择通过支付现金支付 400 美元意外费用的美国人比例从 50% 上升至 63%： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53075fad-8e5b-4d07-8061-93590df71195_555x369.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53075fad-8e5b-4d07-8061-93590df71195_555x369.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53075fad-8e5b-4d07-8061-93590df71195_555x369.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53075fad-8e5b-4d07-8061-93590df71195_555x369.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53075fad-8e5b-4d07-8061-93590df71195_555x369.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53075fad-8e5b-4d07-8061-93590df71195_555x369.jpeg" width="555" height="369" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/53075fad-8e5b-4d07-8061-93590df71195_555x369.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:369,&quot;width&quot;:555,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:45382,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53075fad-8e5b-4d07-8061-93590df71195_555x369.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53075fad-8e5b-4d07-8061-93590df71195_555x369.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53075fad-8e5b-4d07-8061-93590df71195_555x369.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53075fad-8e5b-4d07-8061-93590df71195_555x369.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.federalreserve.gov/publications/2020-economic-well-being-of-us-households-in-2019-dealing-with-unexpected-expenses.htm">FRB</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>只有<a href="https://www.federalreserve.gov/publications/2020-economic-well-being-of-us-households-in-2019-dealing-with-unexpected-expenses.htm">12% 的人表示他们无法支付</a>400 美元的费用。</p><p>现在，12% 的美国人无法支付 400 美元的费用，这远远高于应有的水平！但这与你所看到的声称“靠工资生活”的人数相差甚远。金融不安全是我们绝对应该认真对待的另一个经济问题，但关于危机和衰退的流行叙述被夸大了。</p><h4>新闻越来越负面</h4><p>为什么如此多的负面叙述成为美国新闻观众的普遍看法？我认为，部分原因是 2010 年代末的普遍动荡，部分原因是外部政治派别传递的信息，他们希望通过制造国家陷入危机的感觉来获利。但新闻媒体本身在过去几十年里变得越来越消极。</p><p>宾斯伯根等人。有<a href="https://www.nber.org/papers/w32026">一篇新论文</a>，其中他们使用文本挖掘来分析报纸中使用的语言。他们构建了对经济和非经济新闻的积极与消极情绪的衡量标准。在短期内，他们的经济情绪指标与经济事件相对应——经济衰退或通胀带来负面情绪，经济繁荣带来积极情绪。但从长期来看，经济和非经济景气多年来一直处于下降趋势： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32dc79af-6940-47fc-8039-e3b89af4c7fb_802x710.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32dc79af-6940-47fc-8039-e3b89af4c7fb_802x710.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32dc79af-6940-47fc-8039-e3b89af4c7fb_802x710.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32dc79af-6940-47fc-8039-e3b89af4c7fb_802x710.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32dc79af-6940-47fc-8039-e3b89af4c7fb_802x710.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32dc79af-6940-47fc-8039-e3b89af4c7fb_802x710.jpeg" width="802" height="710" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/32dc79af-6940-47fc-8039-e3b89af4c7fb_802x710.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:710,&quot;width&quot;:802,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:151437,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32dc79af-6940-47fc-8039-e3b89af4c7fb_802x710.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32dc79af-6940-47fc-8039-e3b89af4c7fb_802x710.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32dc79af-6940-47fc-8039-e3b89af4c7fb_802x710.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32dc79af-6940-47fc-8039-e3b89af4c7fb_802x710.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.nber.org/papers/w32026">Binsbergen 等人。 (2024)</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>这里发生了什么？众所周知，<a href="https://www.pnas.org/doi/10.1073/pnas.1908369116">大量</a><a href="https://www.nature.com/articles/s41562-023-01538-4">研究</a>表明，<a href="https://www.vox.com/the-highlight/23596969/bad-news-negativity-bias-media">新闻存在负面偏见</a>——坏消息比好消息更受关注，这使得媒体有动力强调和过度报道坏消息。近年来，随着新闻媒体的竞争越来越激烈，这种趋势可能有所加剧。由于放松管制和新技术而导致的竞争加剧可能迫使报纸为了生存而变得越来越危言耸听和消极。</p><p>我想到的另一个假设是，从地方新闻转向全国新闻可能会导致更多负面消息。我找不到关于当地新闻是否比全国新闻更积极的研究，但人们确实倾向于认为当地经济比全国经济更好： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42b59379-30f2-4532-bf7e-6a0aa74baadf_850x819.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42b59379-30f2-4532-bf7e-6a0aa74baadf_850x819.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42b59379-30f2-4532-bf7e-6a0aa74baadf_850x819.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42b59379-30f2-4532-bf7e-6a0aa74baadf_850x819.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42b59379-30f2-4532-bf7e-6a0aa74baadf_850x819.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42b59379-30f2-4532-bf7e-6a0aa74baadf_850x819.jpeg" width="850" height="819" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/42b59379-30f2-4532-bf7e-6a0aa74baadf_850x819.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:819,&quot;width&quot;:850,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:92951,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42b59379-30f2-4532-bf7e-6a0aa74baadf_850x819.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42b59379-30f2-4532-bf7e-6a0aa74baadf_850x819.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42b59379-30f2-4532-bf7e-6a0aa74baadf_850x819.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42b59379-30f2-4532-bf7e-6a0aa74baadf_850x819.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.theatlantic.com/newsletters/archive/2022/06/american-economy-negative-perception-inflation/661149/">大西洋月刊</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>也许<a href="https://www.axios.com/2023/11/16/newspapers-decline-hedge-funds-research">当地报纸的长期缓慢消亡</a>以及随之而来的新闻国有化正在加剧负面情绪？我认为值得研究一下。</p><h4>经济活动正在遍布美国各地</h4><p>另一个常见的负面说法是，美国人在住房上的支出比以前多得多。这不是真的。杰里米·霍佩达尔 (Jeremy Horpedahl) 在一篇文章中<a href="https://economistwritingeveryday.com/2023/04/26/spending-on-housing-it-hasnt-really-increased-in-the-past-40-years/">揭穿了这个常见的神话</a>。他利用消费者支出调查的数据显示，美国人用于总体住房（包括自住住房）的收入比例多年来一直在下降，而用于住房（即租金）的比例则基本保持不变。平坦的。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9fb13077-e5bb-4324-a3c1-16bd4fd6846f_768x483.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9fb13077-e5bb-4324-a3c1-16bd4fd6846f_768x483.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9fb13077-e5bb-4324-a3c1-16bd4fd6846f_768x483.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9fb13077-e5bb-4324-a3c1-16bd4fd6846f_768x483.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9fb13077-e5bb-4324-a3c1-16bd4fd6846f_768x483.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9fb13077-e5bb-4324-a3c1-16bd4fd6846f_768x483.jpeg" width="688" height="432.6875" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/9fb13077-e5bb-4324-a3c1-16bd4fd6846f_768x483.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:483,&quot;width&quot;:768,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:688,&quot;bytes&quot;:86267,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9fb13077-e5bb-4324-a3c1-16bd4fd6846f_768x483.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9fb13077-e5bb-4324-a3c1-16bd4fd6846f_768x483.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9fb13077-e5bb-4324-a3c1-16bd4fd6846f_768x483.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9fb13077-e5bb-4324-a3c1-16bd4fd6846f_768x483.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：杰里米<a href="https://economistwritingeveryday.com/2023/04/26/spending-on-housing-it-hasnt-really-increased-in-the-past-40-years/">·霍佩达尔</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>但这个故事有一个问题：它没有根据人们居住的<em>地方</em>进行调整。在过去的四分之一个世纪里，生活在旧金山等“超级明星”城市的住房和租金溢价飙升，迫使收入微薄的人们离开这些城市。这意味着美国城市因收入而变得更加隔离，穷人因住房短缺而被排除在最好的居住地之外。</p><p>但这个故事现在可能也开始改变。布鲁金斯学会的 Mark Muro 和 Yang You 的<a href="https://www.brookings.edu/articles/tech-jobs-are-finally-spreading-out-spurred-by-private-investment-and-federal-initiatives/">一份新报告</a>显示，IT 产业正在向全国扩散：</p><p>十多年来，数字活动似乎首次开始蔓延。具体来说，在国家科技行业中所占份额不断增加的都市区名单……现在由一群非超级明星城市主导，这些城市与统治多年的大型科技圣地完全不同……</p><blockquote><p> 2020 年至 2022 年间……旧金山和圣何塞从数字就业比例最高的都市区名单中消失。取而代之的是达拉斯、丹佛、迈阿密和盐湖城等充满活力的<a href="https://www.brookings.edu/articles/superstars-rising-stars-and-the-rest-pandemic-trends-and-shifts-in-the-geography-of-tech/">“后起之秀”都市区</a>……犹他州普罗沃等相对科技较新的都市区跻身近年来数字服务就业份额增长前十名的都市区。田纳西州纳什维尔；休斯顿;和佛罗里达州杰克逊维尔。</p></blockquote><p>部分原因是远程工作的兴起和 2010 年代科技热潮的结束。部分原因是超级明星城市的住房短缺。但 Muro 和 You 将其与产业政策联系起来：</p><blockquote><p> [A] 2021 年，全国各地爆发了令人欢迎的私人投资“大建设”——其中一些是从国外“回流”或“本土化”，有望为“其他领域的崛起”带来好处。自那时起，新的资金激增带来了超过<a href="https://www.whitehouse.gov/invest/">2300 亿美元</a>的私人半导体和电子制造投资以及技术和数字服务支出，其中大部分广泛分布在全县各地。其中许多投资将反过来吸引计算机系统设计等就业密集型辅助行业的其他区域投资……除了私人投资热潮之外，上届国会制定的 38 亿美元里程碑式经济发展立法中的很大一部分还将为政府提供数十亿美元的额外资金（以及私人）投资于中心地带、南部和西部山区的新的和“后起之秀”的都市区。</p></blockquote><p>这种基于地方的产业政策是很多人在 2010 年代所主张的，尤其是当特朗普 2016 年的当选在许多人看来体现了铁锈地带和其他被遗忘的地方的愤怒时。但最终还是拜登政府掏出现金在腹地投资建厂。</p><p>无论如何，如果科技产业确实继续在美国蔓延，那将是一件非常好的事情，即使其中一些是由旧金山等地的高住房成本造成的。它将遵循产业成熟后在全国范围内寻找更便宜土地的历史模式，并且它们的集群效应变得不那么压倒性。</p><h4>企业减税并不像经济学家想象的那么大</h4><p>经济学家<a href="https://home.uchicago.edu/~huhlig/papers/uhlig.trabandt.jme.2011.pdf">多年前就发现</a>，除非税率<em>非常</em>高（就像第二次世界大战后的几年一样），否则削减个人所得税实际上并不能刺激经济。这就是为什么布什00年代初期的减税政策对经济没有起到任何作用，而共和党人也不再强调个人所得税减免作为其经济战略的主要支柱。</p><p>但人们仍然对企业减税有所不同抱有很大希望。 <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Optimal_capital_income_taxation#The_Chamley%E2%80%93Judd_zero_capital_income_tax_result">经济学的一个经典理论</a>表明，对生产性资本的税收应该为零——因为你希望经济积累所需的资本，所以你应该不对它征税，然后对劳动力或消费等其他东西征税。该理论总是有很多假设和警告；事实上，您<a href="https://scholar.harvard.edu/files/straub/files/chamley-judd-revisited_june_2018.pdf">可能应该对资本收入征税</a>。但资本是<em>随着时间的推移而积累起来的生产力</em>这一基本原则仍然表明，我们应该比其他形式的收入更轻地征税。</p><p>因此，经济学家和经济作家有些乐观地认为，唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 2017 年的企业减税政策（将<a href="https://www.investopedia.com/taxes/trumps-tax-reform-plan-explained/">企业税率降至 21%</a> ）将​​给经济带来某种提振。事实上，2010 年代末是经济非常好的年份，认为特朗普的减税政策与此有关并不疯狂。</p><p>但<a href="https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0014292122000885?via%3Dihub#tbl2">Gechert 和 Heimberger 的 2022 年荟萃分析</a>表明，企业减税实际上并没有那么强大：</p><blockquote><p>我们将元回归方法应用于一个新的数据集，该数据集包含来自 42 项初步研究的 441 项估计值。有证据表明，出版物的选择性有利于报道企业减税对增长的促进作用。为了纠正这种偏见，我们不能拒绝公司税对增长零影响的假设。</p></blockquote><p>与许多此类荟萃分析一样，他们有一个“漏斗图”，显示估计值集中在零附近： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ea6aec5-b6f7-453c-a6e2-3a45ca87d8aa_874x805.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ea6aec5-b6f7-453c-a6e2-3a45ca87d8aa_874x805.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ea6aec5-b6f7-453c-a6e2-3a45ca87d8aa_874x805.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ea6aec5-b6f7-453c-a6e2-3a45ca87d8aa_874x805.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ea6aec5-b6f7-453c-a6e2-3a45ca87d8aa_874x805.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ea6aec5-b6f7-453c-a6e2-3a45ca87d8aa_874x805.jpeg" width="874" height="805" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/8ea6aec5-b6f7-453c-a6e2-3a45ca87d8aa_874x805.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:805,&quot;width&quot;:874,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:168827,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ea6aec5-b6f7-453c-a6e2-3a45ca87d8aa_874x805.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ea6aec5-b6f7-453c-a6e2-3a45ca87d8aa_874x805.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ea6aec5-b6f7-453c-a6e2-3a45ca87d8aa_874x805.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ea6aec5-b6f7-453c-a6e2-3a45ca87d8aa_874x805.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0014292122000885?via%3Dihub#tbl2">Gechert &amp; Heimberger (2022)</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>请注意，如果作者不纠正出版偏见，文献发现企业减税确实会促进经济增长，尽管幅度不大。只有当发表偏见得到纠正后，他们才发现根本没有效果。对发表偏差的校正依赖于这样的想法：上面的漏斗图应该是对称的——没有偏差的文献应该有与错误的低估计一样多的错误高估计。基本上，这是一个论点，即我们应该查看模态估计（0 效应处的峰值）而不是平均值。</p><p>我不一定认同这种说法。可能存在方法论偏差，这些偏差往往会可靠地在零附近产生一堆蹩脚的研究，但在其他地方则不然。例如，企业减税可能需要数年时间才能产生效果，因此试图过早寻找效果的研究最终集中在零附近。如果这是真的，那么效应的“真实”分布不应具有零峰值，并且估计的“未经校正”均值更接近事实。</p><p>但即便如此，这种效应规模仍然相当有限——企业减税 10 个百分点，仅能带来 0.2 个百分点的经济增长提振（比特朗普所做的还要大）。<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/what-the-solow-model-can-teach-us">理论告诉我们</a>，增长的推动不会是永久性的，因为经济最终将达到资本水平更高的新稳定状态，此后增长仅取决于技术进步。</p><p>因此，我认为实证文献只是告诉我们，企业减税的力度没有我们想象的那么大。这并不意味着它们毫无用处——特别是对于那些尚不具备大量资本存量的发展中国家而言。但总体而言，我认为有理由认为减税热衷者最后的巨大希望已经竭尽全力。从现在开始，美国应该把重点放在其他促进增长的方法上。 </p><div><hr></div><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?"><span>现在订阅</span></a></p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/at-least-five-interesting-things-7be?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"> <a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/at-least-five-interesting-things-7be?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share"><span>分享</span></a></p><p>PS - 这是我用 GPT-4 制作的更多“战斗兔子”图片： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F17410224-06fc-4a48-8cc2-1d2f53396d6e_1024x1024.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F17410224-06fc-4a48-8cc2-1d2f53396d6e_1024x1024.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post