ding="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.nber.org/papers/w25893">Arora等。 (2019)</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>这项研究不仅对于增加人类知识至关重要，而且对于为私营部门提供动力也至关重要。 <a href="https://twitter.com/emollick/status/1723728219894083830">Tartari 和 Stern（2021）</a>发现，政府向大学提供的每 160 万美元研究资助最终会创造 5000 万美元的创业价值！</p><p>然而，在这段时间里，其他事情已经发生了：研究生产力，通过相对于研究支出的总要素生产率增长的量衡量，一直在稳步下降。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F05fd318a-5101-4641-ba55-a48c51ef066d_1140x674.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F05fd318a-5101-4641-ba55-a48c51ef066d_1140x674.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F05fd318a-5101-4641-ba55-a48c51ef066d_1140x674.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F05fd318a-5101-4641-ba55-a48c51ef066d_1140x674.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F05fd318a-5101-4641-ba55-a48c51ef066d_1140x674.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F05fd318a-5101-4641-ba55-a48c51ef066d_1140x674.jpeg" width="1140" height="674" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/05fd318a-5101-4641-ba55-a48c51ef066d_1140x674.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:674,&quot;width&quot;:1140,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:133385,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F05fd318a-5101-4641-ba55-a48c51ef066d_1140x674.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F05fd318a-5101-4641-ba55-a48c51ef066d_1140x674.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F05fd318a-5101-4641-ba55-a48c51ef066d_1140x674.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F05fd318a-5101-4641-ba55-a48c51ef066d_1140x674.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://web.stanford.edu/~chadj/IdeaPF.pdf">Bloom等。 (2020)</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>现在，这并不意味着研究不再值得花钱（<a href="https://mattsclancy.substack.com/p/what-are-the-returns-to-r-and-d">它</a>）。这也不意味着大学仅归咎于这一趋势，因为它已经到位了，因为在大学占主导地位之前。这在很大程度上可能只是因为想法越来越难找到，或者美国在边际（但仍然有价值）的研究项目上投入了更多资金，或者研究成果没有商业化。</p><p>但是，鉴于大学现在在我们的研究生态系统中发挥的关键作用，并且考虑到心理学，医学和其他经验学科的<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Replication_crisis">复制危机</a>，询问我们的大学是否通过产生太多无用或误导性研究来浪费国家资源是有道理的。</p><p>这是一个痛苦的问题，因为我们很多人（包括我自己）通过学术系统出现，还是在那里工作，或者有朋友和家人在那里工作。鉴于希望以文化战争的理由与研究生产力无关的保守派，许多进步主义者将不安，这是一个不安的问题。但是，无论如何，这都是我们需要提出的问题，因为我们的研究大学中的大量人才集中是我们最有价值的国家资源之一，我们需要考虑我们创造的激励系统是否使该资源充分利用。</p><h4>衡量浪费确实很难</h4><p>量化研究浪费是极其困难的。一种方法是考虑从出版物到应用的研究生产过程中涉及的步骤。马克·安德森（Marc Andreessen）<a href="https://twitter.com/pmarca/status/1743720603214131677">出现了一个细分</a>： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff19cf928-bb42-4c6c-8e1e-cce3972177c3_683x590.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff19cf928-bb42-4c6c-8e1e-cce3972177c3_683x590.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff19cf928-bb42-4c6c-8e1e-cce3972