口，以及2）贫困。非洲的生育率正在缩小，就像其他任何地方一样，但它开始做得很晚。因此，人口势头将使非洲人口达到顶峰时（一些预报员认为会发生在本世纪末左右）。这是<a href="https://www.imf.org/en/Publications/fandd/issues/2023/09/PT-african-century">IMF报告</a>中的信息图： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59545567-eccb-40de-ac4c-f6d0aaf645a5_1855x2457.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59545567-eccb-40de-ac4c-f6d0aaf645a5_1855x2457.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59545567-eccb-40de-ac4c-f6d0aaf645a5_1855x2457.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59545567-eccb-40de-ac4c-f6d0aaf645a5_1855x2457.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59545567-eccb-40de-ac4c-f6d0aaf645a5_1855x2457.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59545567-eccb-40de-ac4c-f6d0aaf645a5_1855x2457.jpeg" width="670" height="887.657967032967" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/59545567-eccb-40de-ac4c-f6d0aaf645a5_1855x2457.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&