过<a href="https://twitter.com/MssZeeUsman/status/1742286799379050759?t=YlwU8i-yVJfWeV21milztg&amp;s=19">Zainab Usman</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>请注意，随着人口增长的减慢，通过<a href="https://www.imf.org/external/pubs/ft/fandd/2006/09/basics.htm">人口红利</a>，这些收益将越来越多地转化为人均生活水平。</p><p>因此，无论如何，非洲对我们的未来仍然非常重要，我继续对此保持谨慎乐观。这是我三年前写的：</p><div><hr></div><p>每隔一段时间，我都有写博客的渴望，所以今天我想我会写关于非洲的文章。</p><p><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Afrofuturism">非洲裔</a>是一个有趣而有趣的科幻小说和哲学流派：但是每当我看到这个词时，我都会笑，因为<em>所有</em>未来主义实际上都是非洲裔。非洲实际上是整个世界的未来。<a href="https://ourworldindata.org/future-population-growth">这</a>是您将看到的两个或三个最重要的图表之一： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3b3a8f0d-4529-4eb8-b2ec-78770f24dad7_1020x720.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3b3a8f0d-4529-4eb8-b2ec-78770f24dad7_1020x720.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3b3a8f0d-4529-4eb8-b2ec-78770f24dad7_1020x720.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3b3a8f0d-4529-4eb8-b2ec-78770f24dad7_1020x720.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3b3a8f0d-4529-4eb8-b2ec-7